eeper low-acceleration\nslope. Improvements in measurements and modelling of the outer Milky~Way, and\nweak lensing, seem like the most promising path toward stronger constraints on\nthe low-acceleration behaviour of the RAR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2020 18:00:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 11:58:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-17"}
