tion data sets\nexhibiting complex geological terrain, with improved accuracy and uncertainty\nquantification in a cross validation study versus two rigid registration\nmethods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2020 22:58:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-15"}
