onical ensemble. A free-energy landscape of\nthe biomolecular system is obtainable from the canonical ensemble.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2020 05:25:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2020 23:26:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-17"}
