ies data by setting relevant parameters and configuration files.\nFurthermore, the tool is approximately 3X faster than methods using relational\ndatabase management systems at matching massive catalogues.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2020 05:56:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 03:36:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-18"}
