 Stack\nOverflow. A small-scale user study demonstrates that our tool is useful for\nassisting developers in finding and using relevant programming tutorials in\ntheir programming tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2020 10:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-15"}
