ong\ncompartments and by constraining the process covariance matrix of the model in\nthis contribution. Applicability of the proposed identification procedure is\ndiscussed in terms of growing state-space and therefore speeding up of the\nidentification algorithm is suggested. Performance of the proposed approach is\ntested and demonstrated on simulated data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2020 13:23:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-15"}
